Management system for a boxing gym

Manage the boxer, trainer and money of the gym.

/*gym*/
Total    //total = Student fee - (Teacher salary + cost)
boxer Fee
boxers
Trainer Salary
trainers
cost     // Cost of running the gym not the salary

/*trainer*/
name
seniority		//new(2 years and less) old(3 years and more)
Hours worked		//minimum 30h max 40h, no overtime
Salary (Hourly)		//new: 2$ old 4$

/*boxer*/
id
name
Fee Total			//200$ or 500$
Fee Payed			//Fee payed to that point
level of the boxer		//beginner(fee is 200$),  intermediate(fee is 200$), professional(fee is 500$): Can do professional fight